{"tid":1155517,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★$4000效應？青年遭數名男子搶劫$4000大元！","createTime":"2019-05-15T04:06:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-15T05:11:43.000Z","uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"16a89b6f7b1b492a6651eaa36080e1c0e31a1110","tid":1155517,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T04:06:14.000Z","msg":"今日(15日)凌晨4時許，一名20餘歲青年途經粉嶺聯和墟聯興街時，遭數名男子毆劫，事主高呼「救命」，賊匪搶走其身上的一部iPhone手機，以及內有約4000港元現金及身份證的銀包後逃去。<br />\n<br />\n由於遇劫事主身上財物盡失，他步至一店舖向職員借了數枚壹圓硬幣，準備往附近電話亭報案，他疑受驚過度，並無向職員求助，以及忘記電話亭打999不需入錢，其後，他步至電話亭投入硬幣報案及致電通知家人。<br />\n<br />\n警方到場調查，遇劫事主受傷，經救護員治理傷勢後，拒絕送院，由警車載返警署。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190515/bkn-20190515053651439-0515_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190515%2Fbkn-20190515053651439-0515_00822_001.html&d=UmPnmdD3xn3sHJtz75hgVw3x%2FUg%2Bgbtl8eFt0uNm3qw%3D&h=810b385e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190515/bkn-20190515053651439-0515_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"c51e34553848c6d13f26054fa0407bc45d007947","tid":1155517,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T04:07:06.000Z","msg":"拖延派$4000 令罪惡滔天 <br />\n<br />\n政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecaca35bbbe38015c5a783261587cf2fdba03147","tid":1155517,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T04:56:52.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"f8a3207cc00568c5df284e3430878c5275a3855a","tid":1155517,"uid":1761,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T04:59:12.000Z","msg":"忘記電話亭打999不需入錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40ebf9fb158efdff059a548f4a4fd7a3130f66bc","tid":11